PHP Libivrt READ ME
-------------------

1) Purpose of this project

This project provides PHP language bindings for Libvirt API... PHP is a scripting language and Libvirt is virtalization framework/API.
For more details see: http://phplibvirt.cybersales.cz/ http://www.libvirt.org/ http://www.php.net/

2) Documentation
Documentation is provided in doc/ directory

